# SCD Type 3

## Definition
Stores limited historical data using extra columns.

## Example
current_city
previous_city

## Key Idea
History stored in columns instead of rows.

## Advantages
- Simple queries
- Easy comparison
- Less storage than Type 2

## Disadvantages
- Limited history
- Not scalable
- Schema changes required

## Difference
Type 2 -> new rows
Type 3 -> new columns
